
<div class="text-center text-black-200 mt-3">
	<h2 class="font-weight-bold">Why does my dog lick me?</h2>

	<div class="text-sm; font-italic">
		A dog life
	</div>
</div>
<div class="container p-1">
	<div class="row pt-4">
		<div class="col-5 ">
